OL,3,CKing sharing his cancer diagnosis 'has
OL,4,Chelped men open up', says BEM recipient
OL,6,FA woman who has been awarded a British
OL,7,FEmpire Medal (BEM) for her work with
OL,8,Fthe cancer charity she co-founded
OL,9,Fafter her twin brother died of the
OL,10,Fillness has said the King being open
OL,11,Fabout his diagnosis "has been really
OL,12,Fgood for men".
OL,14,FJenna Speirs, and her parents Caroline
OL,15,Fand Duncan Speirs, have each been
OL,16,Fawarded a British Empire Medal (BEM)
OL,17,Ffor the work they have done with the
OL,18,Fcharity they started after Jenna's
OL,19,Ftwin brother Calum died of cancer aged
OL,20,F12.
