OL,3,CKing sharing his cancer diagnosis 'has
OL,4,Chelped men open up', says BEM recipient
OL,6,FIt is the first time three family
OL,7,Fmembers have been named in the same
OL,8,Fhonours list.
OL,10,FThe trio, from the Isle of Bute,
OL,11,Fstarted the charity Calum's Cabin
OL,12,Fafter Calum, who had an inoperable
OL,13,Fbrain tumour, died.
OL,15,FOn being named in the King's Birthday
OL,16,FHonours, Jenna, a therapeutic
OL,17,Fradiographer, said Charles sharing his
OL,18,Fcancer diagnosis has helped men open
OL,19,Fup.
