OL,3,CKing sharing his cancer diagnosis 'has
OL,4,Chelped men open up', says BEM recipient
OL,6,F"Him being so open about his cancer
OL,7,Fjourney has been really good for men
OL,8,Fin particular," Jenna said.
OL,10,F"You see a lot of men sitting alone in
OL,11,Fthe waiting rooms, but now they are
OL,12,Fchatting more."
OL,14,FDuring his time in hospital before his
OL,15,Fdeath in 2007, Calum told his sister
OL,16,FJenna, now 30, he wanted to start
OL,17,Fsomething called "Calum's Caravan" for
OL,18,Fchildren with cancer to spend time
OL,19,Faway with their families.
