OL,3,CKing sharing his cancer diagnosis 'has
OL,4,Chelped men open up', says BEM recipient
OL,6,F"We were very fortunate growing up
OL,7,Fgoing on holidays and living on the
OL,8,FIsle of Bute, but lots of children in
OL,9,Fhospital never got to see the outdoors
OL,10,For the sea," Jenna said.
OL,12,F"It was his idea. He wanted people to
OL,13,Fbe able to take time away."
OL,15,FThe Speirs family had planned to start
OL,16,Fthe charity when he recovered from his
OL,17,Fillness.
OL,19,F"Unfortunately, that wasn't to be,"
OL,20,FJenna said. "So we started fundraising
OL,21,Fat his funeral."
