OL,3,CKing sharing his cancer diagnosis 'has
OL,4,Chelped men open up', says BEM recipient
OL,6,FTwo years later, Calum's Cabin had
OL,7,Facquired its first holiday home for
OL,8,Ffamilies of children being treated for
OL,9,Fcancer in Scotland to use.
OL,11,FSince then, thousands of families have
OL,12,Fbeen helped by the charity, which now
OL,13,Fhas several holiday homes as well as
OL,14,Fflats in Glasgow for hospital patients
OL,15,Fand their families to stay in if they
OL,16,Flive further afield.
OL,18,FCaroline, 59, Duncan, 63, and Jenna
OL,19,Fsaid receiving the medals was "very
OL,20,Fspecial" and dedicated them to Calum.
